100191.name: 2012-2013 CTU Open Contest
100191.description:
The CTU Open Contest is a preparation for the CERC. It is a local contest held at CTU Prague and its main goal is to choose the team representing CTU in Central European Regional Contest. To make the competition more interesting, the Contest is open for any Czech university. 
The universities from the Czech Republic are not required to participate in CTU Open Contest. But it is strongly recommended, because the participants of CTU Open will be preferred in CERC if there are too many teams applied. Besides, it is a very good preparation. 
The Contest Rules for CTU Open Contest are the same as CERC Rules. The only exception is that the contest language is Czech.

100486.name: 2014-2015 CT S02E02: Codeforces Trainings Season 2 Episode 2 (CTU Open 2011 + misc)
100486.description:
The CTU Open Contest is a preparation for the CERC. It is a local contest held at CTU Prague and its main goal is to choose the team representing CTU in Central European Regional Contest. To make the competition more interesting, the Contest is open for any Czech university. 
The universities from the Czech Republic are not required to participate in CTU Open Contest. But it is strongly recommended, because the participants of CTU Open will be preferred in CERC if there are too many teams applied. Besides, it is a very good preparation. 
The Contest Rules for CTU Open Contest are the same as CERC Rules. The only exception is that the contest language is Czech.

101505.name: 2016-2017 CTU Open Contest
101505.description:
The CTU Open Contest is a preparation for the CERC. It is a local contest held at CTU Prague and its main goal is to choose the team representing CTU in Central European Regional Contest. To make the competition more interesting, the Contest is open for any Czech university. 
The universities from the Czech Republic are not required to participate in CTU Open Contest. But it is strongly recommended, because the participants of CTU Open will be preferred in CERC if there are too many teams applied. Besides, it is a very good preparation. 
The Contest Rules for CTU Open Contest are the same as CERC Rules. The only exception is that the contest language is Czech.

The universities from the Czech Republic are not required to participate in CTU Open Contest. But it is strongly recommended, because the participants of CTU Open will be preferred in CERC if there are too many teams applied. Besides, it is a very good preparation. 
The Contest Rules for CTU Open Contest are the same as CERC Rules. The only exception is that the contest language is Czech.

105136.description: В каждой задаче содержится 70 тестов помимо тестов из условия. Каждый тест оценивается в 1 балл, если все тесты в задаче проёдены то добавляются ещё 30 баллов. Таким образом по каждой задаче можно получить до 100 баллов. Прохождение тестов из примера является необходимым условием для тестирования. В протоколе тестирования отображаются результаты тестирования на всех тестах до первого не верного, и вердикт на первом не выполненном тесте.
